Author: Matilda Brown
Maintainer: Matilda Brown <matilda.brown@utas.edu.au>
Description: This package contains several functions to extract and describe 
  the morphological characteristics of the leaf epidermis. Features include cell 
  angle, number of stomatal rows, undulation index, maximum amplitude of cell 
  wall undulations. Pavement cells can be separated according to how close to 
  stomata they are. More details can be found in.
